<abstract abstract-type="short" xml:lang="en"><p><![CDATA[Abstract: The article examines five dimensions of cosmopolitan citizenship: the cosmopolitan democratic law; global distributive justice; variables territorial constituencies; global civil society; and cosmopolitan education. It also discusses the normative implications that follow from these understandings. According to the article, cosmopolitan citizenship is a coherent and correct political objective.]]></p></abstract>
